latestIgtvVideos.title: GREEN BEAUTY FT @vanitywagon
SOFT PINK FESTIVE GLAM🌸
LETS TALK PERIODS🤍
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
One of the most significant topics nowadays is environmental pollution, and it is something that we need to talk about rather than avoid. Any product that is made using industrially manufactured plastic takes roughly 1000 years to decompose in landfills.

Do you know, sanitary napkins are mostly made up of plastic and it takes more than 600 years to decompose! Time we switch to organic cotton pads which are 100% biodegradable! I’ve recently tried @hilifewomen organic sanitary napkins and this is something I want to bring to you guys as it is:
- GOTS-Certified Organic Cotton
- Double Airlaid Technology
- Honeycomb Structure
- Magic Holes
- Biodegradable Sanitary Pad Disposal Bag
Happy periods♥️
.
.

There’s something magical about Navdip Tundiya that every textile enthusiast should experience at least once. During my visit, I was captivated by the sheer beauty and craftsmanship of their exclusive Patola and Bandhani designs.

Loved witnessing firsthand the skill and dedication that goes into every piece, and honestly, it was such a joyful experience that I couldn’t wait to capture and share it with you. If you want to truly appreciate the beauty and heritage of Patola, this place should be your next stop! 

It will definitely captivate you🪷

Hyderabad Store:
Plot No 69A, Lane No. 1, MLA Colony, Banjara Hills, Hyderabad, Telangana 500034

Stores: Hyderabad | Surat | Rajkot | Ahmedabad

2nd Saree - @indya - effortless elegance.
